cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use jmpxx, please cite it using this metadata."
title: "jmpxx: non-local, RAII-correct, exception-free error propagation for C++20"
abstract: >-
  A header-only C++20 library for exception-free, RAII-correct, non-local error
  propagation, built for code compiled with exceptions disabled, with zero overhead
  over a hand-written branch verified by committed codegen.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "DimitryQm"
version: 0.1.2
date-released: "2026-06-25"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/DimitryQm/jmpxx"
url: "https://github.com/DimitryQm/jmpxx"
keywords:
  - C++
  - C++20
  - error-handling
  - exception-free
  - RAII
  - embedded
